steps.name: I am an CFA user and Lands on shop page
Navigate to device details page and select pink
Land on the 'Tariffs and extra' page
I Land on the basket page and choose home delivery option
Check for order contract text for DD/PreOrder phone in Basket Page
input TEST and ACCEPTA and other valid details in Delivery page and Click on the 'Continue button'
